description:
Advanced feature: extend InstallMethod to support OS-conditional methods.

Motivation:
- Some Homebrew casks may not work on Linux
- Could skip methods that don't apply to current OS

Proposed schema extension:
{
  'harness.method': {
    ...existing fields...,
    'os': ['macos', 'linux']  // optional, defaults to all
  }
}

This is P2 - only implement if Homebrew-on-Linux issues become noisy.

Reference: docs/preset-rationale.md 'Future Considerations'
